    • createElection

      public static Election createElection​(java.lang.String electionFileName)
      This function takes the file name a ballot CSV file and returns the election object based on that file. If the file cannot be found or has incorrect formatting a statement prints and the program exits.
      Parameters:
      electionFileName - The name of the CSV file with the election data
      Returns:
      An Election object. In this case an OPL or IR Election Object
